description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 49, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 147, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Leverage for East, 8 for South, and 3 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
